     my thing has always been to make the content off youtube, and then post it on youtube (and my website, and maybe other video sites if it makes sense.) i think it's pretty hard to actually make videos ON youtube, you can get much better tools off youtube. but speaking of tools, my previous tools were banished from society because they were too old (that's my mistake, they were already almost banished when i first started using them and i somehow failed to notice) so that's interesting news because now i don't have the old tools but the great news is the new tools are ridiculous. the only problem is it took me years to learn how to use the old tools and it will take me years to learn how to use these. but they are ridiculous. and i'm sure i will start releasing things well before i know what the hell i'm doing. that's just company policy
